##"Do you dare to wear it out the door? " The 90-year-old police angrily asked the mask maker

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

By Zhu Yiyi, thepaper.cn

"Do you dare to wear your mask to go out? Dare? " This is the Shanghai economic detection 90 post-90 police high border to make false criminal suspects, issued a strong query.

On the third day of the Lunar New Year, the police of the food, medicine and Environment Investigation detachment in the home alone suddenly received a phone call from the unit. On the other end of the phone, the head of the detachment told her that there was a case of making and selling fake face masks in the suburbs, and investigators needed to be sent to the scene to handle the case. She couldn't help but express herself readily that she had time and could be present.

Since that phone call, Gao Jing has been working on the front line of the fight against epidemic-related crimes.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Photo courtesy of the Shanghai police

Many of the days and nights spent in supermarkets, pharmacies, neighborhoods, office buildings or factory buildings in remote suburbs, she joked, were "people who moved around during the epidemic. ".

Let Gao Jing impression is the most impressive, is his participation in the investigation of a large production, sales of fake and inferior mask case. Gao Jing remembers it was Valentine's Day, and as she was getting off work, she suddenly got a phone call about a counterfeiting operation in a house in Songjiang District.

The police car sounded the Siren, and Gao Jing hung up with his colleagues and went on his way. "When we arrived at the scene, we saw a modest-looking two-story farm house, but I was completely shocked when we entered the back room, " he said, the so-called mask pressure molds and vent valves are thickly covered with cobwebs, and dozens of snakeskin bags of finished masks are stacked haphazardly in the attic, tied up with the loose ear straps of the masks, all in and out of the police and market supervision personnel, clothes are stained with the white dust can not be beat.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
At present this pair of"dirty mess"the scene, how can produce make mask? But the criminal suspect also disapprovingly expresses to this "anyway protects the function to be similar" . Gao Jing questioned him at the scene, "do you dare to wear the mask you do out? Dare? " Just also eloquently suspect moment silence. Eventually, she and her colleagues smashed the den, the scene seized more than 100,000 counterfeit brand masks, as well as a large number of counterfeit raw materials and counterfeit tools.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Retrograde in the first line of the epidemic, the high environment is not afraid, she has also been in the suspect sent to the medical examination process, when the other side is in a high fever state when the heart tight. But more often than not, this short-haired, clean-cut girl from the 1990s has no age or gender tag, and like countless "economic scouts, " she fights fearlessly at the forefront of the fight against economic crime.

This issue is edited by Yu Hua Zhou
